&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Product Manager at Very Good Ventures, you will be responsible for how we strategically engage with our clients, guiding the creation of meaningful, impactful products and business outcomes, and ensuring that we deliver client success, client satisfaction and world-class user experiences. You will bring to the table a wealth of experience with different Product Management and strategic frameworks and methodologies, and collaborate with cross-functional teams to define product strategy, prioritize product requirements, and lead the end-to-end product development lifecycle, all while aligning with our clients&#39; business goals and growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a self-motivated and influential individual who can operate with a high degree of autonomy while working effectively to build strong relationships and help drive both delivery outcomes and ongoing commercial success. As a Senior Product Manager, you will be an integral part of our organization, shaping and defining the success of the product management discipline and sharing accountability of client success through account management and growth. This position requires a flexible mindset, strong leadership and communication skills, and a deep understanding of business, strategy, design, and technology. This is an onsite role based at our client&#39;s Philadelphia office. Candidates must be located in the Philadelphia area or within a 90-minute commute, or be willing to relocate prior to their start date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
